==English==
===Tag===
'''[[don't]]/[[doesn't]]''' ''one'''''?'''<BR>
'''doesn't [[one]]?'''

# ''[[request|Request]] for [[confirmation]] that converts an affirmative present tense sentence into a [[question]]. Expects [[agreement]] in a "yes" answer.''
#:<tt>“</tt>You like ice cream, '''don't you'''?<tt>”</tt>

====Usage notes====
As a tag, always used with an object pronoun substituting for the subject. Number distinguishes ''do'' versus ''does''.

